Inhlolisiso le ikhangele njalo isimo samalungelo oluntu emhlabeni jikelele. Emhlubulweni wezansi yezwekazi leAfrica, linhlanganiso ithe abalwela amalungelo bahlukuluzwe kakhulu ngohulumende babo ngo2017. Umqondisi weAmnesty International eZimbabwe, uMnu Cousin Zilala usole uhulumende weZimbabwe esithi wephula ilungelo loluntu mihla lamalanga lanxa nje ekulandula lokhu. Kodwa uZilala uthe ukugenqulwa kukaMugabe embusweni libutho nyakenye kulethe ithemba lokuthi ukuhlukuluzwa okugoqela ukubotshwa lokutshaywa kwabantu abaphikisana lohulumende kuzahlehla.
